  "original_title": "\u0b9a\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bcb\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc8 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bc6\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc7\u0bb1 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0baf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0bae\u0bc7\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd 67 \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Another 67 people were arrested for trying to leave the country illegally",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Sri Lanka Navy today arrested 67 more people who tried to leave the country illegally by sea.",
        "Today (08) in the morning, during the patrolling operation carried out by the navy in Kalmunai East Coast, the said crew was arrested along with a fishing boat.",
        "The Sri Lankan Navy conducts routine operations and patrols covering the maritime and coastal areas around the country with the objective of controlling illegal immigration and other illegal activities.",
        "Accordingly, a suspected local fishing trawler carrying this group of 67 people, while patrolling at Kalmunai this morning, was intercepted and arrested by the Sri Lankan Navy who tried to leave the country illegally by sea.",
        "In this case, 53 men including 06 smugglers, 06 women and 08 children were among those arrested. The fishing trawler used for this illegal activity has also been seized by the navy.",
        "The arrested have been identified as belonging to Mannar, Vavuniya, Mullaitivu, Trincomalee and Batticaloa, aged between 01 and 56 years."
      ],
